# Hopewell Hall

## The Heart of Camp Otyokwah

Hopewell Hall is our main gathering facility — a spacious, fully equipped venue that brings your whole group together for meals, worship, meetings, and celebration.

---

## Facility Features

- **Dining Capacity**: 260 guests seated for meals
- **Meeting Capacity**: 90 for conference or seminar-style setup
- **Stage**: Raised stage for speakers, bands, and performers
- **Projector & Screen**: Built-in projection system for presentations and media
- **A/V Equipment**: Full audio/visual system included
- **Climate**: Fully air conditioned for year-round comfort
- **Kitchen**: Adjacent full commercial kitchen

---

## Commercial Kitchen

Our commercial kitchen is equipped to serve your entire group with quality, nourishing meals.

### Full Catering Service
Our kitchen staff prepares delicious meals served family-style. All meals are prepared on-site with accommodations for dietary restrictions.

### Self-Catering Option
Bring your own team and use our commercial kitchen facilities for full meal preparation.

### Custom Menus
Work with our staff to create menus tailored to your event and group preferences.

---

## Dietary Accommodations

We do our best to accommodate various dietary needs, including:
- Food allergies
- Vegetarian options
- Religious dietary restrictions
- Medical dietary needs

---

## Multiple Uses

Hopewell Hall is more than a dining room. It easily transforms into:
- Large group plenary and session space
- Evening program venue
- Banquet and celebration hall
- Worship and gathering space
- Rainy-day activity hub

---

